  "1886080": {
    "name": "Tetraphobia",
    "steam_appid": 1886080,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1886080/extras/1126dc937c5db3265dc69bd3a7a988ae.poster.avif?t=1708531337\" width=600 height=256 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1886080/extras/1126dc937c5db3265dc69bd3a7a988ae.webm?t=1708531337\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1886080/extras/1126dc937c5db3265dc69bd3a7a988ae.mp4?t=1708531337\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>。<br><br>Tetraphobia 是一款roguelite 动作射击游戏，它将地牢爬行游戏的体验带到了天空中。游戏中，玩家将扮演一名手持变身弓的寻宝流氓 Trixx，在一个按程序生成的浮岛世界中战斗，岛上到处都是危险的生物和强大的泰坦巨人。<br><br>您的变形弓可以在长弓和短弓之间随意切换，为您提供不同的战斗策略。您可以使用短弓射击、躲闪和轰击敌人的营地，也可以从远处使用长弓进行穿甲冲锋。<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>与凶猛的泰坦战斗</strong></h2><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1886080/extras/130176db499e075e3e856b17e4328383.poster.avif?t=1708531337\" width=600 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1886080/extras/130176db499e075e3e856b17e4328383.webm?t=1708531337\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1886080/extras/130176db499e075e3e856b17e4328383.mp4?t=1708531337\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>碎裂的天空》的背景是一个美丽的浮岛世界，灵感来自东亚奇幻风格，是一个危险的地方，人们可能会屈服于自己的恐惧。四位泰坦守护着整个世界的不同领域，每个领域都有自己独特的身份。不同的领域会有独特的敌人、BOSS 和大量独特的工艺品。<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>具有强大效果的激动人心的神器</strong></h2><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1886080/extras/27e98ceece0d61eea46c84f151eb600a.poster.avif?t=1708531337\" width=600 height=256 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1886080/extras/27e98ceece0d61eea46c84f151eb600a.webm?t=1708531337\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1886080/extras/27e98ceece0d61eea46c84f151eb600a.mp4?t=1708531337\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>。<br><br>Tetraphobia 拥有多个独特的区域、种类繁多的人工制品、令人兴奋的修改器和不为人知的秘密--《Tetraphobia》充满了胭脂般的细节，让每次运行都充满新鲜感和独特性。根据您访问的地区和发现的秘密，您可能会得到一把令人难以置信的大弓、强大的盟友或一支小猫军队。<br><br>如果您发现的文物与您当前的装备不匹配，您可以在飞艇岛进行交易。<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>猎取猫食</strong></h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1886080/extras/7e280ae8437aa98e70604ae95daca32f.poster.avif?t=1708531337\" width=600 height=256 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1886080/extras/7e280ae8437aa98e70604ae95daca32f.webm?t=1708531337\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1886080/extras/7e280ae8437aa98e70604ae95daca32f.mp4?t=1708531337\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>。<br>当然，您在《破碎的天空》中能找到的最重要的战利品就是猫粮！这些喵星人的杰作将让您有机会从您的猫同伴雷诺身上找到额外的战利品。至于它为什么不直接把战利品送给你，这还是个谜。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1886080/extras/7c332fb1c38dc2d53cf7e7b8e45aa8f9.poster.avif?t=1708531337\" width=600 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1886080/extras/7c332fb1c38dc2d53cf7e7b8e45aa8f9.webm?t=1708531337\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1886080/extras/7c332fb1c38dc2d53cf7e7b8e45aa8f9.mp4?t=1708531337\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>。<br>在整个旅途中，你会拯救其他被恐惧吞噬的人。一旦获救，他们将让你获得更高级的人工制品和独特的修改器，这些东西会以不同的方式影响《破碎的天空》。有些人还会向你提出独特的挑战和任务，并给予独特的奖励，让你的旅程更加刺激。",
